- Located in packages/gateway/src/channels/registry.ts

2. Council System
- Multi-agent debate and consensus mechanism
- Role-based evaluation with specialized perspectives
- Weighted voting system with confidence scoring
- Located in packages/brain/agent/council.py

## Knowledge Management (Score: 80)
