- Time-based decay system for node relevance
- Custom traversal algorithms for context retrieval
- Located in packages/brain/agent/memory_graph.py

2. Evidence Chain
- Auditable decision trails with categorized evidence
- Relevance scoring and chain building
- Located in packages/brain/agent/evidence.py

## Execution & Security (Score: 85)
1. Agent Execution System
- Sandboxed skill execution environment
